### Quick start

```bash
# 1. Build the prototype-deployer image & push it (only once)
cd simple_deployer
docker build -t host.docker.internal:6789/simple_deployer:latest .
docker push host.docker.internal:6789/simple_deployer:latest

# 2. Point the inventory at your cluster (local Minikube or remote)
vim ansible/inventory/hosts.yaml      # adjust kubeconfig or SSH details

# 3. Edit or duplicate an experiment vars file
vim ansible/experiments_vars/teastore/vars.yaml      # or copy to experiments_vars/other_sut/vars.yaml and edit there

# 4a. Run the default experiment ("teestore")
ansible-playbook -i ansible/inventory/hosts.yaml ansible/deploy.yaml

#   Run different experiment (other_sut, etc.)
ansible-playbook -i ansible/inventory/hosts.yaml \
                 -e "experiment_name=other_sut" \
                 ansible/deploy.yml
